{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require online knife purchases to be collected in-person from the Post Office.",
        "additional_details": "We believe a lot of violence with knives comes from the use of kitchen knives. We  think that this policy could help give police a better chance to prevent crime from occurring.",
        "background": "We urge the Government to require the purchase of knives online to be collected in-person from the post office, with purchasers required to provide two types of ID, to help identify if people are providing false documents.",
